{"results":[{"aya":"043","id":1845,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"火狱必定是他们全体的约定的地方。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"044","id":1846,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"火狱有7道门，每道门将收容他们中被派定的一部分人。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"045","id":1847,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"敬畏者们必定在一些乐园和源泉之间，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"046","id":1848,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"你们平平安安地进入乐园吧！","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"047","id":1849,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"我清除他们胸中的怨恨，他们将成为弟兄，在高榻上相对而坐。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"048","id":1850,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"他们在那里不感觉疲乏，他们绝不被逐出。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"049","id":1851,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"你告诉我的仆人们，我确是至赦的，至慈的；","translator":"Ma Jian"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":15,"previousPage":"/zh/s015-6.json","nextPage":"/zh/s015-8.json"}}